mpany made up of four (4) individuals - (i) the Chief Executive Officer of HOFV, (ii) the Chief Executive Officer of PFHOF, (iii) the Chief Executive Officer of the Village Media Company and (iv) the Executive Director of the HOF Media Company; provided, that if the Chief Executive Officer of the Village Media Company and the Executive Director of the HOF Media Company are the same individual (as is expected as of the Effective Date), then the fourth member of the Advisory Board shall be appointed by unanimous agreement of the foregoing individuals. The Advisory Board's function shall be to facilitate the consideration of opportunities presented to either or both of the Village Media Company and the HOF Media Company.

