e receipt and sufficiency of which is hereby acknowledged, the Parties   hereby agree as follows:   ARTICLE I   DEFINITIONS   1.1 Definitions. For purposes of this Agreement, the following terms shall have the following meanings, and to the extent   not defined in this section or otherwise in this Agreement, a term shall have the meaning ascribed to it in any of the Other   Agreements:   Source: CONFORMIS INC, 10-Q, 11/1/2019



